## Output Format
Write in clean **markdown**. Show the actual copy (not descriptions of copy).
Every headline must pass the "so what?" test. Every CTA must be specific
(e.g. "See Your Custom Quote" not "Learn More"). Write copy that sounds
like it came from one brand — not generic ChatGPT filler.
